1) For each (cmdb_id, kpi_name) compute global P5 (5th percentile) on the full series and attach it to metrics_summary as p5_value (do not recalculate P95; reuse p95_value there).
2) Filter metric.csv to the incident window: timestamps between 2020-05-28 03:30:00+08:00 and 2020-05-28 04:00:00+08:00 inclusive.
